<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FAQs</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.1/css/all.min.css">
	<link href="~/css/faq.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h2>For any queries, look up here</h2>
        <div class="dark-line"></div>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#registration">> Registration Process</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">> Trek Facilities</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">> Payment Issues</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">> Cancellation</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">> Women Safety</a></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="dark-line"></div>
        <div class="accordion">
            <h2>Registration Issues</h2>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                    <span>How Do I Register for a Trek</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>Our registration process is entirely an online process. You'll be able to complete it in a few simple steps:</p>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Head to the upcoming treks page and choose a trek.</li>
                        <li>Click on View Dates and select a date of your choice. Then click on Book.</li>
                        <li>Create an account for yourself if you don’t already have one.</li>
                        <li>If you want to add people for your trek you can add</li>
                        <li>Make the payment online.</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                    <span>Can I book my slot without paying for a Trek</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>No, slots are confirmed only after the payment is completed to ensure fairness and availability for all participants.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                    <span>Can I register for Solo trip</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>Yes, solo trips are welcome. Many solo travelers join us for treks, and it's a great way to meet like-minded people!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!---------->
        <div class="dark-line"></div>
        <div class="accordion" id="facilities">
            <h2>Trek Issues</h2>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                    <span>How many trekkers stay in a tent?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>Each tent accommodates 3 trekkers comfortably.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                    <span>What is the group size on an Indiahikes trek?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>Our groups usually have around 20-25 trekkers to ensure everyone has a personalized and enjoyable experience.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                    <span>Can I change my pickup location?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>No, you can't' change your pickup location.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                    <span>What are the toilets/washroom facilities like on the trek?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>We provide separate toilet tents for men and women with basic hygiene facilities.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                    <span>Can I carry my laptop on the trek?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>We recommend not carrying laptops on treks to avoid damage or added weight.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                    <span>Can I get a separate room at the basecamp for an additional cost?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>No, separate rooms are available at an additional cost.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                    <span>Is smoking and drinking allowed while on trek?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>No, smoking and drinking are strictly prohibited during the trek to ensure safety and health.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                    <span>What will happen if I am not fit for the trek?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>If you are deemed unfit during the trek, our trek leaders will ensure you safely return to the basecamp. No compromises are made on safety.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="dark-line"></div>
        <!----------->
        <div class="accordion" id="facilities">
            <h2>Payment Concerns</h2>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                    <span>My transaction failed. What should I do?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>If your transaction failed, check your bank account to confirm if the amount was debited. Retry after some time or contact our support team for assistance.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                    <span>My amount got debited, but I did not get a confirmation. What should I do?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>If the amount was debited but no confirmation was received, please email us at <strong>TrekMastersIndia@gmail.com</strong> with the transaction details.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                    <span>What payment modes do you accept?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>We accept payments through credit/debit cards, net banking, UPI, and digital wallets.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                    <span>Do you accept partial payments?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>Currently, we accept only full payments to confirm your trek booking.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                    <span>Can I pay through EMI?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>Unfortunately, we do not have EMI options. Only single-time payments are accepted.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="dark-line"></div>

            <!-- Cancellation Section -->
            <div class="accordion" id="cancellation">
                <h2>Cancellation</h2>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <div class="accordion-header">
                        <span>What is your cancellation policy?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-content">
                        <p>Our cancellation policy varies based on how far in advance you cancel. Please refer to our cancellation terms for detailed information at <strong>https://localhost:7133/Home/Cancellation</strong>.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <div class="accordion-header">
                        <span>How many days in advance should I cancel my trek?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-content">
                        <p>It’s best to cancel at least 30 days before the trek for a partial refund. Refund policies are stricter for last-minute cancellations.To know about refund policies checkout at <strong>https://localhost:7133/Home/Cancellation</strong></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <div class="accordion-header">
                        <span>How do I cancel my trek?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-content">
                        <p>To cancel your trek, log in to your account, go to 'My Treks,' and click on the cancellation option for the trek you booked.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <div class="accordion-header">
                        <span>How long does the refund process take?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-content">
                        <p>Refunds are processed within 7-10 working days after cancellation.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="dark-line"></div>

            <!-- Women Safety Section -->
            <div class="accordion" id="womenSafety">
                <h2>Women Safety</h2>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <div class="accordion-header">
                        <span>How safe are Indiahikes treks for women?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-content">
                        <p>Indiahikes treks are highly safe for women. We ensure equal treatment, separate toilet facilities, and a strong code of conduct among participants.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <div class="accordion-header">
                        <span>Can I trek when I'm menstruating? Can I trek with periods?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-content">
                        <p>Yes, you can trek during your periods. Ensure you carry proper sanitary products, and our staff will assist with any needs or concerns.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <div class="accordion-header">
                        <span>How is the tent sharing?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-content">
                        <p>Tents are shared between 2-3 trekkers of the same gender unless you're trekking with family or friends.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>



        <script>
            document.querySelectorAll('.accordion-header').forEach(header => {
                header.addEventListener('click', () => {
                    const content = header.nextElementSibling;
                    header.classList.toggle('open');
                    content.classList.toggle('open');
                });
            });
        </script>
</body>
</html>